DMA hardware automatically clears the corresponding DCRn[EEXT] bit when the byte count register reaches zero</description>
                        <bitOffset>7</bitOffset>
                        <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
                        <enumeratedValues>
                           <enumeratedValue>
